DialogueNode.dialogue: Not much, it's been a slow day so far. How have you been?
Well Sharon, I was actually wondering if we could talk about something.
I'm just fine, thanks for asking! Nobody asks how I'm doing these days.
I really should be getting back to work though...
Wait, could you actually spare a minute? There's something I wanted to talk to you about.
No worries! I'll see you around, Sharon.
I've actually received a few reports of gender discrimination.
Is this something you've noticed lately?
Oh... Well, I wasn't expecting that. But I can't say it comes as a surprise...
I don't want to say too much, but I will say that some of the male employees around here don't have enough respect for their female coworkers.
Is there anything else you could tell me?
Could you give me any names?
Player, I really don't want to get caught up in this. Maybe you could try talking to someone else.
Okay. Thank you for your time, Sharon.
